 ["でもミサトさんは", "きっと"]}, {"box": [75, 100, 184, 271], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["必死で僕を", "なぐさめようと", "する"]}, {"box": [501, 372, 596, 489], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["そしたら", "僕はもっと", "つらくなる"]}, {"box": [643, 518, 701, 658], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ミサトさんも", "悲しんでる"]}, {"box": [886, 769, 945, 908], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ミサトさん", "だけじゃない"]}, {"box": [620, 839, 721, 1008], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["きっと", "他の人もみんな", "悲しんでる"]}, {"box": [441, 793, 475, 850], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["でも"]}, {"box": [499, 1138, 670, 1306], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["そんなところへ", "行っても", "綾波の死を", "思い知らされる", "だけだ"]}, {"box": [150, 1125, 249, 1316], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["ひとりでいるのは", "おし潰されそうで", "もっと怖い"]}], "img_path": "090.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1024, "img_height": 1454, "blocks": [{"box": [866, 117, 928, 258], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["だからここが", "いいんだ"]}, {"box": [380, 134, 416, 232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["君だけは"]}, {"box": [119, 504, 228, 668], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["綾波のことで", "心を痛めてない", "から"]}, {"box": [903, 756, 922, 833], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["くく．．．"]}, {"box": [654, 775, 689, 971], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["あははは．．．"]}, {"box": [400, 1215, 432, 1313], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["あはは"]}], "img_path": "091.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1024, "img_height": 1454, "blocks": [{"box": [786, 116, 892, 357], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["僕のことは嫌いだけど", "ここは居心地いいって", "ワケ？"]}, {"box": [455, 109, 561, 278], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ずい分", "おもしろいこと", "言うね"]}, {"box": [336, 440, 405, 542], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["勝手に", "すれば？"]}, {"box": [857, 765, 897, 842], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["勝